cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.AI, cs.DS, cs.CE 

This paper deals with predicting conversion rates in display advertising, which involves machine learning and data analysis. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.IR (Information Retrieval) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also involves statistical analysis and modeling, which could fall under cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) and cs.CE (Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science).
